commit.message:
compress.c (write_data): Mark 'ze' as unused.

	* compress.c (write_data): Mark 'ze' as unused.
	* jartool.h (__attribute__): New define.
	* shift.c (shift_up): Added cast.
	(shift_down): Likewise.
	* jartool.c (help): Split string constant.

From-SVN: r107681

+	* jartool.h (__attribute__): New define.
+	* shift.c (shift_up): Added cast.
+	(shift_down): Likewise.

 2005-06-29  Kelley Cook  <kcook@gcc.gnu.org>
